Security Layer: 4-digit reversed-password authentication ("6452") with masked asterisk input.

Power Management: Independent control for Air Conditioning, Power Outlets, and Lighting.

Programmable Shutdown: Custom timer function (1â€“9 minutes) using the 8253 PIT for delayed branch shutdown.

Hardware Interface: Direct port-mapped I/O for real-time status updates.
